  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras/d52a498d3bb5dfcbc2402d7da3f80cdf.avif?t=1756764173\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras_big/d52a498d3bb5dfcbc2402d7da3f80cdf.avif?t=1756764173 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Entity Strike is a 2D top-down survival game and the debut project of a passionate indie developer.</strong> <br>Face chaotic hordes of entities in a dark, devastated world. Get ready for intense combat, strategic upgrades, and a relentless, fast-paced experience. Built from the ground up with love and ambition, this game invites players to be part of its journey from the very beginning. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras/7ab7ad71fea2447eda09d364c4b3ea90.avif?t=1756764173\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras_big/7ab7ad71fea2447eda09d364c4b3ea90.avif?t=1756764173 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frenetic combat against dozens of enemies at once.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic upgrade system: build your loadout before the run and evolve it during gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive dark atmosphere with lighting effects based on player actions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new abilities by completing specific objectives in each run.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras/80f93452e9d62b308bfe25bfecfc4936.avif?t=1756764173\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras_big/80f93452e9d62b308bfe25bfecfc4936.avif?t=1756764173 width=800 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 Survival is just the beginning</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the new Score Store system, every run contributes to your permanent progression. Earn points, unlock powerful meta upgrades, and strengthen your character between sessions. Perfect for fans of Vampire Survivors, Brotato, 20 Minutes Till Dawn, and other roguelikes with long-term progression.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras/1576a5a110880ca59a46363d9618d87d.avif?t=1756764173\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras_big/1576a5a110880ca59a46363d9618d87d.avif?t=1756764173 width=800 height=452 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras/d52a498d3bb5dfcbc2402d7da3f80cdf.avif?t=1756764173\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras_big/d52a498d3bb5dfcbc2402d7da3f80cdf.avif?t=1756764173 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Entity Strike is a 2D top-down survival game and the debut project of a passionate indie developer.</strong> <br>Face chaotic hordes of entities in a dark, devastated world. Get ready for intense combat, strategic upgrades, and a relentless, fast-paced experience. Built from the ground up with love and ambition, this game invites players to be part of its journey from the very beginning. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras/7ab7ad71fea2447eda09d364c4b3ea90.avif?t=1756764173\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras_big/7ab7ad71fea2447eda09d364c4b3ea90.avif?t=1756764173 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frenetic combat against dozens of enemies at once.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic upgrade system: build your loadout before the run and evolve it during gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive dark atmosphere with lighting effects based on player actions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new abilities by completing specific objectives in each run.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras/80f93452e9d62b308bfe25bfecfc4936.avif?t=1756764173\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras_big/80f93452e9d62b308bfe25bfecfc4936.avif?t=1756764173 width=800 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 Survival is just the beginning</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the new Score Store system, every run contributes to your permanent progression. Earn points, unlock powerful meta upgrades, and strengthen your character between sessions. Perfect for fans of Vampire Survivors, Brotato, 20 Minutes Till Dawn, and other roguelikes with long-term progression.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras/1576a5a110880ca59a46363d9618d87d.avif?t=1756764173\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685980/extras_big/1576a5a110880ca59a46363d9618d87d.avif?t=1756764173 width=800 height=452 /></span></p>",
